oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Ministry of Agriculture and Forestry in Finland
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The Ministry of Agriculture and Forestry's Department of Agriculture creates the operating conditions for the development of Finnish agriculture and horticulture, for safe and high-quality foodstuffs production and for the diversification of the countryside and its industrial structure.
